<br>
&lt;Thurfiz' Kin&gt;<br>
<br>
-----------------------------------------------<br>
For the Impatient:<br>
-----------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
We are an all gnome guild on tallon zek. <br>
  <br>
  * We roleplay (keep in character) as often as possible.<br>
  * We enjoy PvP against Darks and dishonorable lights.<br>
  * We raid mostly on thursday nights and sunday nights, though most of us are casual gamers and stay around level 45 or so.<br>
  * We are ALL short and mostly gnomes. Gnomes are encouraged (mostly required) to take the last name &quot;Halliwax&quot; as surname since we are all related.<br>
  * For info, email &quot;aenrune@triad-dev.com&quot; or visit our website at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://thurfizkin.4t.com">thurfizkin.4t.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<br>
---------------------------------------------<br>
All the Details....<br>
---------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
The Halliwax Family, known as &lt;Thurfiz' Kin&gt;, being decended from the Great Thurfiz Halliwax, have been prowling the Tallon Zek server for going on 3 years. We are one of the oldest, and perhaps oddest <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> , guilds on the server. Currently we are also one of the ONLY and probably the BEST short guilds on the server.<br>
<br>
If you are unfamiliar with Tallon Zek, let me say this. Tallon Zek is a Team PvP server. There are four teams. Short, Human, Elf and Dark.  Short team is allwed Dwarf, Halfling, and GNOME characters.  However, since SOE has not made it impossible to heal/help other teams, &quot;Cross teaming&quot; (grouping/guilding with other teams) runs rampant.<br>
<br>
Not only is Thurfiz' Kin one of the only short guilds on the entire server (we allow only shorts and mostly gnomes) but we are one of the funnest!<br>
<br>
Our website (<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://thurfizkin.4t.com)">thurfizkin.4t.com)</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> abounds with the lore and micheif that our Gnomes and friends get into. Stories and parties are just as part of our lives as leveling and PvPing.<br>
<br>
<br>
An important point to remember is that we are &quot;family&quot; not just &quot;guildies&quot;. We treat each other as family, and all Gnomes take the proud last name &quot;Halliwax&quot;. Actually there is kind of a ritual where you petition for the name... There are so many Halliwax's on the server, that you cannot get the last name unless you summon a GM. hehe.<br>
<br>
Also, if you are thinking of rolling a Gnome, I have a whole host of names reserved that are &quot;hallwaxish&quot;. See, not only do we bear the same last name, but our FIRST names are all similar as well! Ex. Merliben, Darliben, Arliben, Dwarliben, Berae, Beralle, Erae, Lemalle, etc.<br>
<br>
<br>
---------------------------------------------<br>
About you...<br>
---------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Do you like roleplay? Maybe even interested in PvP? ( though this is not a requirement of the guild) Like a fun, casual atmosphere filled with cheerie gnomes?<br>
<br>
Maybe you should give us a try!  Most of our members actually came from other servers to be part of this, and heck! MOst of us are only level 38-45!  We play casually so it makes a great alt guild especially if you can make the &quot;family nights&quot; on Thursdays and Fridays!!<br>
<br>
<br>
Stop on by and say hullo!<br>
<br>
Merliben Halliwax<br>
